  "title": "Automation Engineer",
  "description": "<p>Job Description & Requirements</p><p>• Define specifications and scope of work to contractors.</p><p>• Start up, testing, commissioning, and troubleshooting of machines.</p><p>• Responsible for Single Line Drawing, Control Schematic drawings, and programming of PLC/HMI</p><p>• Execute project in a timely manner.</p><p>• Preparation and support installation team.</p><p>• Willing to travel and work on overseas projects.</p><p><br /></p><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><p>• Minimum 3-5 years relevant working experiences in automation.</p><p>• Programming knowledge and experience on Siemens PLC and WinCC.</p><p>• Knowledge in design of control panels.</p><p>• Knowledge on control, schematics, motor controls and materials take off.</p><p>• Possess good communication and interpersonal skill.</p><p>• Able to take on numerous challenging tasks while simultaneously meeting high standards and deadlines/vision.</p><p>• Able to take on ownership of tasked jobs.</p>",
